00023Er 2               
00023Er 2               		/*
00023Er 2               		A & $2002 -> set Z(zero flag)
00023Er 2               		$2002 bit7(vblank) -> N(negative), bit6(sprite 0 hit) -> V(overflow)
00023Er 2               		Reset vblank & sprite 0 hit flag
